divs: Sighting DetailsMy son and I were throwing the football and the object caught my eye because how fast it was moving. Planes regularly come through the airspace in our neighborhood. This was moving at least twice as fast as any jet. The object was a bright white dot. Best I can describe is a white M&M moving across the sky. Weird!
